{"page_content": "![](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/_assets/3137b1a864c689786cac76b3def62dd1/Assets/img/default-banner.jpg)\n\n# Mechanical Inspection and Maintenance of Heavy Vehicles\n\nIn order to ensure that heavy vehicles are in good mechanical condition, the SAAQ administers regulations and programs that allow for interventions in several areas.\n\n#### Buses and minibuses\n\nOwners, operators and drivers of buses and minibuses must also comply with the requirements concerning vehicle maintenance and making sure they are in good condition, as these vehicles are considered heavy vehicles.\n\nLast update: May 17, 2022\n\n## Safety first, on the road and online\n\nWe are committed to protecting your personal information and privacy. That's why, when we collect data, we follow a [Policy on Privacy](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/policies/privacy) that is responsible and transparent. By continuing to browse without modifying your preferences, you accept the use of cookies.\n\nEdit settingsAcceptReject\n\nDÃ©tection du zoom", "metadata": {"title": "Mechanical Inspection and Maintenance of Heavy Vehicles - SAAQ", "description": "In order to ensure that heavy vehicles are in good mechanical condition, the SAAQ administers regulations and programs that allow for interventions in several areas.", "url": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/transportation-goods/mechanical-inspection-and-maintenance", "language": "en", "keywords": null, "robots": null, "og_title": "Mechanical Inspection and Maintenance of Heavy Vehicles", "og_description": "In order to ensure that heavy vehicles are in good mechanical condition, the SAAQ administers regulations and programs that allow for interventions in several areas.", "og_url": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/transportation-goods/mechanical-inspection-and-maintenance", "og_image": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/_assets/3137b1a864c689786cac76b3def62dd1/Assets/img/og.png", "og_audio": null, "og_determiner": null, "og_locale": null, "og_locale_alternate": null, "og_